Myth: **The Shared Meal**

After months of tiny, anonymous exchanges at the bridge—a grain, an acorn, a river stone—Lyra arrived one morning to find the farmer sitting there. Not hiding, not leaving things in darkness. Just sitting, watching the dawn.

